- have used spring-boot to set-up this project
- following this http://spring.io/guides/gs/spring-boot/
- added javaplex-4.2.1.jar as dependency in build.gradle file
- then:  >gradle eclipse
  (this produces .classpath for eclipse)
- >gradle build      builds the project into a jar in build-folder
- to run, run from eclipse Application or from console >gradle run
- added application.properties to set port, ...
